What's New

 


HoloWWW Services web-hosting services now support speeds up to 15 megabits per second. For HoloWWW pricing information, please visit the HoloWWW rates page.


Aaddzz, another service of IAT, Inc., is a new web-based advertising network with advanced features for both webmasters and advertisers.

Older News
HoloNet Members can now apply for a Custom Domain Name via the web using our on-line application within the HoloNet Member Administration pages.
HoloWWW service now supports Instant Stores. Instant Stores allows the sale of goods or access to protected Web pages without any CGI programming. HoloWWW service also supports secure transactions,credit card transactions.
